Join the stars with the @amaralegal virtual concert. Amara Legal is an amazing organization that provides legal services to individuals who have been victimized by human trafficking. Check out the information below.  ・・・
#repost @amaralegal 
Let’s have a good time for a good cause! There’s still a few weeks left to get your ticket for Amara’s Star Night In. Donate and get access to the virtual benefit concert featuring talent like Grammy-award winning singer @lisaloeb and comedian and Daily Show writer @joshjohnsoncomedy. You might even win a raffle prize too! Make your donation and get your ticket via the link in our bio.
